characters.title: Portia Duvall
characters.description: Portia Duvall finds herself in a most peculiar situation: her recently deceased daddy left her a mine alongside an incredible amount of debt. Stubborn and naive, she decides to hold on to her inheritance and offers the bandit leader that is here to collect a ... unique solution to her problem.
